name: Parts of the Whole
description: Surrealistrasyon//Şerif Gümüşbaş//Digital Art//1500x1500 pixel//Everything is the struggle of non-relationships to form a whole. And the respect our mind shows for this effort is consciousness and the reality created by consciousness//Drawing is an impressive language for me with its universal and differentiating structure in every viewer. I also love and use the automatism method because it is a pleasant and mysterious way to express myself and what I perceive about existence, the world, and life.
